{
  "stem": "14897.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I married an American man, which is, as a matter of fact, rather rare among survivors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was the best thing for me to have done.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because until then, I was very much connected to my experiences.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I was in Israel, people always-- everybody had somebody whom they lost.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody wanted to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It kept me on the subject, even when I was in school at Columbia University.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had many friends.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had many friends who were American by then, but also friends who were Jews, Polish Jews, survivors, refugees.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I belonged to a-- an interfaith club at Columbia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was still-- I belong to [NON-ENGLISH], which was a Zionist club.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was still very connected to the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But when we married and moved to Buffalo, by necessity, I had a new family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had a different job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I-- I-- that's when I started teaching.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I taught for two years in a college in Buffalo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And after that, I had my family retired and brought them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I brought up my family-- removed me from it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I suppose I-- perhaps I took the easy way out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I tried not to think about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Gradually, it became somewhat dreamlike.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And probably, it helped me to survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And probably, it help-- it helped also my children who, although they considered me always very domineering and bossy-- [LAUGHS] which I am-- did not have quite the syndrome that we have since read about the children of survivors.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You know, they did not feel the guilt because I did not live the guilt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know, maybe it's there somewhere in my personality, but I don't feel it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's hard to tell because I was a child when it started.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
